narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A great class for heritage speakers.
Highly recommended to heritage speakers looking to quickly and thoroughly improve their Spanish. Make sure to participate in class.
Yes, I would recommend it. It is a great way to improve your spanish, especially if your coming in with problems associated with heritage speakers.
it's a great course for heritage speakers. definitely recommend it. will help you improve your spanish through individualized assignments. great professor.
I would definitely recommend it. It helps reintroduce native speakers to grammar structures.

Spanish for Heritage Speakers is a class specially tailored to meet the needs of heritage speaker, language learners. Professor Alexandrov does a great job teaching the course, incorporating interesting activities and discussions, an engaging novel, and interesting films and other materials. I would definitely recommend the course- you learn a lot, and the professor is really wonderful.
